---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "CueCard Blog - Speaker notes, teleprompter tips, and presentation workflows"
description: "Read the CueCard blog for speaker notes tips, teleprompter workflows, and presentation best practices across Zoom, Google Meet, and Teams."
keywords: "cuecard blog, speaker notes tips, teleprompter tips, presentation workflows, zoom speaker notes, google meet notes, teams presenter notes"
canonical: "https://cuecard.dev/blog/"
ogTitle: "CueCard Blog"
ogDescription: "Speaker notes tips, teleprompter workflows, and presentation best practices."
ogImageWidth: "1280"
ogImageHeight: "640"
ogLocale: "en_US"
---
{% block body %}
{% set downloadHref = "/#download" %}
{% include "partials/nav.njk" %}

<main class="blog-page">
    <header class="blog-hero">
        <p class="blog-eyebrow">CueCard Blog</p>
        <h1 class="blog-page-title">Speaker notes that stay invisible.</h1>
        <p class="blog-page-subtitle">
            Practical guides for presenters, educators, and teams who want clean screen shares and confident delivery.
        </p>
    </header>

    <section class="blog-list">
        {% for blog in blogs %}
        <article class="blog-entry">
            <header class="blog-entry-header">
                <p class="blog-meta">
                    <time datetime="{{ blog.datetime }}">{{ blog.datetime }}</time>
                    <span class="blog-meta-separator">&middot;</span>
                    <span class="blog-author">{{ blog.author }}</span>
                </p>
                <h2 class="blog-entry-title">
                    <a href="/blog/{{ blog.slug }}/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ blog.title }}</a>
                </h2>
            </header>
            <div class="blog-entry-content">
                {{ blog.content | markdownExcerpt | safe }}
            </div>
            <a class="blog-entry-link" href="/blog/{{ blog.slug }}/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read full post</a>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
    </section>

    <section class="blog-cta">
        <h2 class="blog-cta-title">Download CueCard</h2>
        <p class="blog-cta-subtitle">Choose the desktop app or the mobile teleprompter.</p>
        <div class="blog-cta-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/#download">Download for Desktop</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/mobile/">Download for Mobile</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

{% include "partials/footer.njk" %}
{% endblock %}
